      "text": "Illegal alien Wenceslao O. Panameno was deported back to El Salvador by ICE in 2017 following a DUI and five-year sentence for RAPING A CHILD in Massachusetts.\n\nThen, a 2025 ICE tipline call led our Boston officers and HSI special agents to a residence where they reintroduced themselves to Panameno, who says he snuck in using a passport with someone else’s name. \n\nHe’s now back in our custody following a year in prison for illegal reentry and will be deported soonest.\n\n📞Your tips make America safer: (866) 347-2423.",
